{"title":"离太阳最近的人——给孔繁森","authors":["孙世平"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":5,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"离太阳最近的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给孔繁森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙世平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一种声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比诗歌更生动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一种色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比画面更传神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旭日从海洋升腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原离蓝天最近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就行走于潮头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就伫立在峰顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从阿里到聊城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从东海到珠峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们呼喊着你的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水和泪水竞相奔涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从妇女到儿童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从孩子到老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家传诵着你的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵与心灵不再陌生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人都是血肉之身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁没有六欲七情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你两度入藏十几载"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次梦中泪染衣襟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离别诚然苦痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相聚纵然欢欣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但风中雨里的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更愿踏辉煌的人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论乡村还是城镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论雪山还是田埂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走到哪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里都是阳光和春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探贫苦视灾情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访孤寡问疾病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把满腔的热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给了边关的父老乡亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你很“傻”也最清醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你很“穷”又是富翁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你视钱财如粪土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把情感当黄金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有人能否定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无私无畏的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的人都敬佩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是人民公仆的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢相信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个地委书记会没钱用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不敢相信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂的高干以卖血助人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的祖国大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有许多您这样的共产党人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但也有一些“蛀虫”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人感到失望和痛心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗与光明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来就是矛盾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美与丑善与恶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一天停止过斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功臣或者罪人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无须包装和吹捧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史是人民写的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民是历史的天平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望永恒的星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅怀不朽的英灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们记住了你的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党人孔繁森"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}